{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/2021/12/14/npm-bbon-react-calendar-package/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"<bbon />","siteUrl":"https://bbon.me"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2b8f3299-ae49-5f6a-8a82-e175d017c4bf","excerpt":"npm (scoped) npm Build and tag publish NPM 타입스크립트로 작성된 리액트 달력 컴포넌트입니다. peer dependencies react NPM GitHub react-dom NPM GitHub dayjs NPM GitHub…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@bbon/react-calendar\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/@bbon/react-calendar\" alt=\"npm (scoped)\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@bbon/react-calendar\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/@bbon/react-calendar\" alt=\"npm\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bbonkr/react-calendar/actions/workflows/build-and-tag.yml\"><img src=\"https://github.com/bbonkr/react-calendar/actions/workflows/build-and-tag.yml/badge.svg\" alt=\"Build and tag\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bbonkr/react-calendar/actions/workflows/publish-npm.yml\"><img src=\"https://github.com/bbonkr/react-calendar/actions/workflows/publish-npm.yml/badge.svg\" alt=\"publish NPM\"></a></p>\n<p>타입스크립트로 작성된 리액트 달력 컴포넌트입니다.</p>\n<h2>peer dependencies</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>react <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/react\">NPM</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react\">GitHub</a></li>\n<li>react-dom <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-dom\">NPM</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react\">GitHub</a></li>\n<li>dayjs <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/dayjs\">NPM</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/iamkun/dayjs\">GitHub</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save @bbon/react-calendar</code></pre></div>\n<h2>사용</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useCallback <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Calendar <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@bbon/react-calendar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@bbon/react-calendar/dist/calendar.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">MyComponent</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> handleChangeSelection <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>start<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> end<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Selected dates: '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> start<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> end<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Calendar\n                useMoveToYear\n                useMoveToMonth\n                highlightToday\n                showDate\n                onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleChangeSelection<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 238px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f7b53d9c414e4354cbe863244945e7d8/7ec08/example-001-238x300.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 125.9493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"렌더링 결과\"\n        title=\"렌더링 결과\"\n        src=\"/static/f7b53d9c414e4354cbe863244945e7d8/7ec08/example-001-238x300.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f7b53d9c414e4354cbe863244945e7d8/ff44c/example-001-238x300.jpg 158w,\n/static/f7b53d9c414e4354cbe863244945e7d8/7ec08/example-001-238x300.jpg 238w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 238px) 100vw, 238px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>모양</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">@bbon/react-calendar/dist/calendar.css</code> 파일의 내용을 확인하고, 스타일을 재정의해서 사용하실 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>시연</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://bbon.me/react-calendar\">bbon.me: react-calendar</a> 로 이동해서 동작을 확인하실 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>번들러</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://webpack.js.org\">Webpack</a> 에서 <a href=\"https://rollupjs.org/\">Rollup</a> 으로 변경했습니다.</p>\n<p>변경사유는 아래와 같습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>트리쉐이킹 (Tree-shaking) 지원</li>\n<li>CommonJS 모듈과 ES 모듈을 모두 제공</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"NPM @bbon/react-calendar package","date":"December 14, 2021","description":null,"categories":["blog","computing","repository"],"tags":["github","github-repository","npm","react","typescript"],"github":{"owner":"bbonkr","repo":"react-calendar"},"featuredImage":null,"draft":null,"comments":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021/11/24/다국어-지원-next-js-웹-응용프로그램/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"다국어 지원 next.js 웹 응용프로그램","draft":null,"comments":null,"featuredImage":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021/12/15/change-the-web-application-target-framework-from-net-5-to-net-6/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Change the web application target framework from .NET 5 to .NET 6","draft":null,"comments":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"2b8f3299-ae49-5f6a-8a82-e175d017c4bf"